overview: ShoXC was a mixed martial arts series produced by the mixed martial arts organization EliteXC, Showtime and Proelite.com. The purpose of the show is to highlight up and coming MMA fighters. The fifth edition of ShoXC took place on March 21, 2008 on Showtime at the Chumash Casino in Santa Ynez, California.
title: ShoXC 5: Denny vs. Malaipet
